features.text:
I'm a digital artist shaping the Metaverse for a living.

Building virtual places, creating avatars and handcrafting cool looking wearables for people to use.
Welcome to my CV gallery, enjoy my collection and my creations.
Our mission is to build the coolest Metaverse and to achieve it I count with an amazing team of artists and developers.
I'm the founder and director of Polygonal Mind, independent creative development studio, based in Zaragoza, Spain.
Our work is already present on many layers of the metaverse  such as Decentralad, CryptoVoxels, VRChat and Beat Saber.
We're always open for work, so if you look to build a high quality experience, gallery, virtual game, avatars or anything cool, feel free to reach out to us, we'll be glad to help you.
